    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Ningyo Clan</p><p>Your Hair and Skin have a scaely finish to them, naturally shiny and slippery finish, that many find unique and pretty</p><ul><li>You have gain +1d4 Bonus to Charisma check and saving throws while not in dim light or darkness.</li><li>You have advantage on rolls made to end the Restrained Condition</li><li>The first time you are hit with a melee attack per turn, the target must make dexterity saving throws vs your Genjutsu Save DC. On a Fail, They are knocked prone.</li></ul>",
